---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Engagement Models & Pricing - intelio" description="Clear engagement models and pricing. Build + Maintain, Build + Operate, or Custom Systems—priced to scope, not packages.">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION WITH BACKGROUND IMAGE -->
  <section class="hero-pricing min-h-screen flex items-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image/Video -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-slate-900" style="z-index: 0;">
      <!-- You can add a video or image here for professional/business/architecture theme -->
    </div>
    
    <!-- Dark Overlay for text readability -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 z-[1]"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.1] tracking-[-1px] text-white mb-6">
          Engagement Models & Pricing
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-4">
          Clear structures. No surprises. Priced to scope.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-white/60 mb-8">
          Intelio engages through a small number of clearly defined models—each designed to reduce friction, create leverage, and align systems with how your business actually operates.
        </p>
        <a href="#pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
          See the Models
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Pricing Tier Cards -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white" id="pricing">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1: Identify + Build + Maintain -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" id="build-maintain">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Identify + Build + Maintain</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Strong systems. Internal ownership.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">For teams that want control without technical burden.</p>
          
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-sm">What's Included:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Business and system assessment
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Architecture and system design
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Implementation and integration
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Documentation and team training
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Ongoing maintenance, updates, and support
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-6">You operate the systems day-to-day. We ensure they stay healthy, aligned, and current.</p>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-center text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Get Custom Quote
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Identify + Build + Operate (FEATURED) -->
        <div class="border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-2xl p-8 relative shadow-lg ring-2 ring-blue-100" id="build-operate">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-4 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full">
            Most Popular
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 mt-2">Identify + Build + Operate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Execution off your plate.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">For teams that need leverage without adding headcount.</p>
          
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-sm">What's Included:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Everything in Build + Maintain
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Ongoing system operation
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Workflow execution and monitoring
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Exception handling and optimization
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Regular performance review and adjustment
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-6">You set direction and priorities. We execute inside the system with full visibility.</p>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-center text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Get Custom Quote
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Custom & Advanced Builds -->
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" id="custom">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Custom & Advanced Builds</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">For complex environments.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">When standard systems break down.</p>
          
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-sm">What's Included:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Selective engagements only
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Custom system architecture
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Advanced AI and automation layers
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Multi-department integration
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              Designed for long-term operation
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-6">Reserved for organizations operating at scale or complexity where off-the-shelf tools are insufficient.</p>
          
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white text-center text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Schedule Discovery
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: How Pricing Is Determined -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">How Pricing Is Determined</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl">
        Pricing is based on scope, not packages. Every engagement begins with understanding what needs to be built.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Left Column: Build Cost Factors -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Factors that influence build cost</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Number of systems being addressed (revenue, operations, finance, etc.)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Complexity of current state (migrating from chaos vs. optimizing existing systems)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Integrations required (CRMs, accounting software, scheduling tools, existing platforms)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Timeline requirements</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Monthly Cost Factors -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Factors that influence monthly cost</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Maintain only vs. active operation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Support response expectations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Ongoing optimization scope</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>Number of users and systems under management</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What's Included in Every Engagement -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">What's Included in Every Engagement</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl">
        Regardless of model, every Intelio engagement includes:
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Discovery and system assessment</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Architecture documentation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Implementation with your tools</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Team training and handoff</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Post-launch support period</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Direct access to senior team</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">No offshore handoffs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Systems designed for long-term ownership</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quote Callout -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 font-medium leading-relaxed">
          "We translate business needs into working systems—applying AI and automation only where they create real leverage."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: Pricing Questions FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">Pricing Questions</p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <div class="faq-card bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 cursor-pointer transition-all">
          <p class="faq-question font-medium text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">Can the build fee be split?</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="faq-chevron w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden text-sm text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
            Yes. Standard terms are 50% at kickoff, 50% at go-live. Alternative structures available for larger engagements.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="faq-card bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 cursor-pointer transition-all">
          <p class="faq-question font-medium text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">When does the monthly fee start?</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="faq-chevron w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden text-sm text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
            Monthly fees begin at go-live, not during the build phase.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="faq-card bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 cursor-pointer transition-all">
          <p class="faq-question font-medium text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">What if my needs change after we start?</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="faq-chevron w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden text-sm text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
            Scope changes are quoted as add-ons or expansions. We don't surprise you with hidden costs.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="faq-card bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 cursor-pointer transition-all">
          <p class="faq-question font-medium text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">Is there a minimum commitment?</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="faq-chevron w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden text-sm text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
            Build + Maintain has no long-term commitment after the build phase. Build + Operate typically requires a 6-month minimum to ensure stability.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 5 -->
        <div class="faq-card bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 cursor-pointer transition-all">
          <p class="faq-question font-medium text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">What if I'm not sure which model fits?</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="faq-chevron w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden text-sm text-gray-600 border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
            Start with a discovery call. We'll assess your situation and recommend the right fit—or tell you if we're not the right partner.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GRADIENT CTA SECTION -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 via-blue-600 to-blue-700 rounded-3xl p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white mb-4">Ready to Talk Scope?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 mb-4">
          Every engagement starts with understanding how your business actually operates. From there, we determine what needs to be built and which model fits.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-8 text-sm">No pressure. No generic pitch. Just clarity.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
          Schedule Discovery Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-pricing {
    background: #000000;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* FAQ Accordion Styles */
  .faq-card.active .faq-answer {
    display: block !important;
  }

  .faq-card.active .faq-chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-card:hover {
    border-color: #3b82f6;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // FAQ Accordion Functionality
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqCards = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-card');
    
    faqCards.forEach(card => {
      card.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const isActive = this.classList.contains('active');
        
        // Close all cards
        faqCards.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));
        
        // Open clicked card if it wasn't active
        if (!isActive) {
          this.classList.add('active');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>

